        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-cyan-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Transaction Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We understand real estate timelines, contingencies, and the importance of clear communication with all parties involved.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-100 to-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
