            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fast Response Times</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We know you can't wait weeks for inspections. Our team prioritizes realtor requests and delivers quick turnarounds.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-100 to-teal-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
